From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Crelia <crelia@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Mon, 1 Jan 2024 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] NeoForge Crop, Loot, Attribute, Crafting, and Entity Capability
 Hooks

Injects NeoForge hooks for:
- CropBlock.grow — canCropGrow / fireCropGrowPost
- StemBlock.grow — canCropGrow / fireCropGrowPost
- BonemealableBlock — fireBlockGrowFeature / fireBonemealEvent
- AlterGroundDecorator.place — alterGround
- LootTable.getRandomItems — modifyLoot (global loot modifiers)
- LootDataType.deserialize — loadLootTable (LootTableLoadEvent)
- DefaultAttributes.getSupplier — getAttributesView / modifyAttributes
- CraftingContainer — setCraftingPlayer / getCraftingPlayer
- AbstractContainerMenu.doClick — onItemStackedOn
- AnvilMenu — fireAnvilCraftPre/Post (additional events)
- GrindstoneMenu — onGrindstoneTake
- Player.drop — onPlayerTossEvent
- ServerPlayer.setGameMode — onChangeGameType
- LivingEntity.shouldTriggerItemUseAnimation — canContinueUsing
- Player.awardStat — onStatAward
- PlayerAdvancements.award — onAdvancementEarnedEvent / onAdvancementProgressedEvent
- ServerLevel.tickCustomSpawners — getCustomSpawners
- GameRules.set — onGameRuleChanged
- LivingEntity.dropAllDeathLoot — onLivingDrops (crafting context)
- EnchantmentMenu.clickMenuButton — onEnchantmentLevelSet
- Entity.canDestroyBlock — canEntityDestroy
- Zombie.canDestroyDoor / Enderman.canDestroyBlock — canEntityGrief
- Animal.tame — onAnimalTame
- Slime.remove — onMobSplit
- ItemEntity.playerTouch — fireItemPickupPost
- LivingEntity.swapHandItems — onLivingSwapHandItems
- LivingEntity.addEffect — canMobEffectBeApplied
- LivingEntity.onClimbable — isLivingOnLadder
- LivingEntity.getVisibilityPercent — getEntityVisibilityMultiplier
- ServerPlayer.sendRecipes — sendRecipes
- ServerGamePacketListenerImpl.handleChat — onServerChatSubmittedEvent
- ServerGamePacketListenerImpl — onCustomClickAction
- OverworldData.save/load — writeAdditionalLevelSaveData / readAdditionalLevelSaveData
- EntityDataSerializer — getSerializer / getSerializerId
- LiquidBlockContainer — canCreateFluidSource
- PortalForcer — onTrySpawnPortal
- ServerEntity.sendPairingData — onStartEntityTracking / onStopEntityTracking
- Level.playSound — onPlaySoundAtEntity
- Level.playSeededSound — onPlaySoundAtPosition
- Player.checkFallDamage — onPlayerFall
- Player.stopSleeping — onPlayerWakeup
- PlayerList.load — firePlayerLoadingEvent
- PlayerList.save — firePlayerSavingEvent
- PlayerList.respawn — firePlayerRespawnPositionEvent
- ServerLevel.advanceDayTime — onSleepFinished
- ServerPlayer.getDisplayName — getPlayerDisplayName
- ServerPlayer.getTabListDisplayName — getPlayerTabListDisplayName
- Player.getDisplayName — getPlayerDisplayName
- BlockState.use — onToolUse
- Level.gameEvent — onVanillaGameEvent

This is a comprehensive catch-all patch for all remaining NeoForge hooks.
